p.k: When the kingdom runs out of inspiration, Unikitty takes it on herself to re-inspire the citizens. / The gang is taking an airplane trip together, and Hawk is at the helm since today he's taking his captain's license test. / Concerned about Puppycorn's propensity to hurt himself constantly, the gang places him into Richard's old Safety Suit. / Unikitty and the gang have crashed on a fabulous island. / The gang are at the local laundromat cleaning their clothes, when Unikitty finds Batman's uniform mixed in with her clothes.
